_sText:
**This map:**

- Medium sized fun/semi-serious/bomb defuse map 
- Fast-paced, well balanced 
- Secret areas included. Can you find them all? 
- Radar + 3d skybox 
- 64 players for large servers 

This map is decompile protected. By downloading, you understand that this map is NOT open sourced, and to not attempt a decompile.

--------------------------

If anyone has any suggestions, please post them below as they can only improve the maps that I produce. Thank you for playing my map :)

***UPDATED 5/4/12 - THIS SHOULD BE FINAL*** 

- Added radar 
- Fixed a few last minute lighting & cubemap issues 
- Modified the secrets slightly. Play to find out!
